    • Constructor Detail

      • ClassifiedJoke

        public ClassifiedJoke(Joke joke,
                      Vocabulary vocabulary)
        Processes a joke with known rating. In addition, it extracts all its words along with their frequencies in the wordPartition Map. It may use stemming and it may ingore the words with length < 3 depending on the booleans ignoreSmall and withStemming from the vocabulary.
        Parameters:
        joke - The current classified joke.
        vocabulary - Vocabulary containing all the words contained in a joke from the training set.
